---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Data Deletion" description="Request deletion of your data from ChefBouyon and Scaling Legends applications.">
  <main style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem 1rem; color: #e0e0e0;">
    <h1 style="color: #e94560; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Data Deletion Request</h1>
    <p style="color: #888; margin-bottom: 2rem;">Last updated: March 14, 2026</p>

    <section style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
      <h2 style="color: #fff;">How to Request Data Deletion</h2>
      <p>If you have used our Facebook or Instagram app and would like to have your data deleted, you can request deletion by following the steps below.</p>
    </section>

    <section style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
      <h2 style="color: #fff;">Option 1: Email Request</h2>
      <p>Send an email to <a href="mailto:chiefbala@gmail.com" style="color: #e94560;">chiefbala@gmail.com</a> with the subject line "Data Deletion Request" and include:</p>
      <ul style="padding-left: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.8;">
        <li>Your full name</li>
        <li>The email address associated with your Facebook/Instagram account</li>
        <li>A brief description of the data you want deleted</li>
      </ul>
      <p style="margin-top: 1rem;">We will process your request within 30 days and confirm deletion via email.</p>
    </section>

    <section style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
      <h2 style="color: #fff;">Option 2: Remove via Facebook</h2>
      <p>You can also remove our app's access to your data directly from Facebook:</p>
      <ol style="padding-left: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.8;">
        <li>Go to your Facebook <a href="https://www.facebook.com/settings?tab=applications" style="color: #e94560;">Settings &gt; Apps and Websites</a></li>
        <li>Find "ChefBouyon" in the list</li>
        <li>Click "Remove"</li>
        <li>Check the box to delete all data the app may have received about you</li>
        <li>Click "Remove" to confirm</li>
      </ol>
    </section>

    <section style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
      <h2 style="color: #fff;">What Gets Deleted</h2>
      <p>Upon receiving your request, we will delete:</p>
      <ul style="padding-left: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.8;">
        <li>Any personal profile data obtained through Meta login</li>
        <li>Custom audience data associated with your account</li>
        <li>Pixel interaction data linked to your profile</li>
        <li>Any other personally identifiable information we hold</li>
      </ul>
      <p style="margin-top: 1rem;">Anonymized, aggregated analytics data that cannot identify you may be retained.</p>
    </section>

    <section style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
      <h2 style="color: #fff;">Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions about data deletion? Email <a href="mailto:chiefbala@gmail.com" style="color: #e94560;">chiefbala@gmail.com</a></p>
    </section>
  </main>
</Base>
